{"tid":2145983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府：美國公開官員資料 將與私隱專員公署商討","createTime":"2020-08-08T10:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T16:38:19.000Z","uid":7542,"like":152,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"dcba40ea44e30f684a83fb703da7b3e4717940f0","tid":2145983,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>希望私隱專員嚴正執法！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特區政府嚴厲批評美國所謂制裁，形容為無恥和卑劣，嚴厲譴責美國政府故意公開官員的個人資料，會保留採取法律行動權利。行政長官林鄭月娥質疑，美方把官員用於申請訪美簽證的資料，作入境以外的用途，指有否違反人權保障，值得商榷。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞表示，有關制裁完全不會影響他，亦批評美國公開官員資料，表示會與私隱專員公署商討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542590-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542590-20200808.htm&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=3e0197f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542590-20200808.htm&h=c2411a90\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542590-20200808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c0f33f7865632d7ff61f8d40cf1c64cfb94e4729","tid":2145983,"uid":130996,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"比明朝既劍斬清朝既官更搞笑<br />\n仲唔叫班黑警捉侵侵番黎"},{"pid":"2cf8717915938ed25693c7fd06fada49287a19c7","tid":2145983,"uid":101481,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:15:03.000Z","msg":"全力支持香港政府制裁美國"},{"pid":"fed9209d1f9771f79c38a3215796177ee460b689","tid":2145983,"uid":333752,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"dcba40ea44e30f684a83fb703da7b3e4717940f0","tid":2145983,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>希望私隱專員嚴正執法！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br